                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8964" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2249</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1010 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工富则价值创——富创精密的人才激励之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Creating value by enriching employees - Fortune Precision’s talent incentive approach</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙新波，楼雨亭，何志伟（通讯作者），郑广文，张浩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">沈阳富创精密设备股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">知识型员工；协同激励；精密制造；激励之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Knowledge Workers; Synergy Incentive; Precision Manufacturing; Incentive Approach</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">半导体设备零部件是集成电路（IC）装备制造环节的硬件基础，在整个半导体产业链中占据重要地位。富创精密专注半导体设备精密制造领域，经过多年发展，现已成为国内规模最大、产品种类最全的半导体设备零部件供应商。作为企业最重要的资源，知识型员工在富创精密发展过程中的作用不可忽视。本案例描述了富创精密通过各种激励措施强化知识型员工工作主动性，从而推动企业克服成长道路上的阻力，不断发展壮大的过程。案例中富创精密在不同阶段发展形成了包括文化建设、班组PK、创新大赛、多通道晋升机制、先进评选、奖牌系统以及工匠专家与企业院士评选等在内的一系列激励措施，持续激发其工作热情。该案例旨在帮助学生掌握知识型员工特征与激励要素等关键知识点，了解并学会运用相关激励理论进行分析，并其培养综合概括和理论联系实践的能力。同时，引导学生更好地理解员工需要以设计有针对性的激励措施提升员工的工作积极性。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Semiconductor equipment parts are the hardware foundation of IC manufacturing and occupy an important position in the whole semiconductor industry chain. Fortune Precision has focused on the precision manufacturing of semiconductor equipment. After years of development, it has become the largest and most complete supplier of semiconductor equipment parts in China. As the most important resource of an enterprise, knowledge-based employees played an important role in the development of Fortune Precision. This case describes the process of Fortune Precision’s overcoming the resistance on the road of growth and continuously developing through various incentives to enhance knowledge-based employees’ work initiative. In this case, Fortune Precision has developed a series of incentives at different stages of development, including culture construction, team PK, innovation contest, multi-channel promotion mechanism, advanced selection, medal system, and the selection of craftsmen experts and enterprise academicians, etc., continuously motivate employees to work. This case aims to help students acquire the key knowledge points of knowledge-based employees’ characteristics and motivational elements, understand and learn to analyze relevant motivational theories, and cultivate the ability of comprehensive generalization and theory-to-practice. At the same time, it guides students to better understand the needs of employees in order to design targeted incentives to enhance employee motivation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">知识型员工激励；协同激励；综合激励理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
